      Classics              : Exhaustive review of basic grammar. Further development of vocabulary, syntax, and style through close readings of selected texts focusing on classical Attic prose.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Lynn Kozak (Fall)                  </p>

    
          <ul class="catalog-notes">
              <li>Prerequisite: CLAS 220 or permission of instructor, minimum grade for prerequisite is B+</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

  </div> <!-- /.node -->
              </div>
            </div>
