      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Classics              : The reading of selected texts in Greek Philosophy Prose in the original Ancient Greek.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Martin Sirois (Fall)                  </p>

    
          <ul class="catalog-notes">
